title: Google parent company Alphabet announces massive $5bn share buyback
text:
Google parent company Alphabet announces massive $5bn share buyback 
The Telegraph Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Google , has announced it will spend over $5bn (?3.3bn) on an enormous share buyback, the first time the company has returned some of its swelling cash pile to shareholders....
